---
title: (Vegetarian) Mediterranean Haloumi, Pesto & Onion Jam Burger with Golden Potato Wedges
description: We’re so excited about this burger! Crispy chunks of squeaky level one haloumi and bold pesto on a baked roll will delight your tastebuds. And along with a side of golden potato wedges? Let’s just say you won’t need the local pub’s burger menu on hand when you’ve got this recipe under your belt.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b6a889a30006c42b71c01d3-77b42a89.jpg
